channel.title: Comments on: Show and Tell at API Wars and Facebook Garage

item.title: By: Conor O'Neill
item.dc:creator: Conor O'Neill
item.description: Thanks Colm, the local developer interest in Facebook seems to have had another big boost with Connect. The opening up of the Live Feed has a lot of people excited too. Looking forward to Thursday.
item.content:encoded: Thanks Colm, the local developer interest in Facebook seems to have had another big boost with Connect. The opening up of the Live Feed has a lot of people excited too. Looking forward to Thursday.

item.title: By: Colm Long
item.dc:creator: Colm Long
item.description: Great to see signups going so well and the event getting so much interest. The facebook team is really looking forward to it. Big thanks to John Kennedy at silicon republic for the coverage.
item.content:encoded: Great to see signups going so well and the event getting so much interest. The facebook team is really looking forward to it. Big thanks to John Kennedy at silicon republic for the coverage.
